description: Ashes to ashes; what your ashes teach you about the cigar you are smoking. We light up the La Flor Domincana and Julius Ceaser by Diamond Crown Cigars, rated 94 in Cigar Jounral. Plus Old Fart Fredy and Debonaire Cigar and Rum's Gentleman's Way.
